This paper focuses on building effective interview chatbots using AI technologies, which involves natural language processing and human-computer interaction. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The paper also discusses the practical design implications for chatbot platforms and empathetic chatbots, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
